The '''2003 Grand Prix Hassan II''' was a [[tennis]] tournament played on [[Clay court|outdoor clay courts]] at the [[Complexe Al Amal]] in [[Casablanca]] in [[Morocco]] and was part of the [[ATP International Series|International Series]] of the [[2003 ATP Tour]]. The tournament ran from April 7 through April 13, 2003.

==Winners==
===Men's Singles===
{{main|2003 Grand Prix Hassan II &ndash; Singles}}
{{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Julien Boutter]]''' defeated {{flagicon|MAR}} [[Younes El Aynaoui]] 6&ndash;2, 2&ndash;6, 6&ndash;1
* It was Boutter's only title of the year and the 5th of his career.

===Men's Doubles===
{{main|2003 Grand Prix Hassan II &ndash; Doubles}}
{{flagicon|CZE}} '''[[Franti<U+0161>ek <U+010C>erm<U+00E1>k]]''' / {{flagicon|CZE}} '''[[Leo<U+0161> Friedl]]''' defeated {{flagicon|USA}} [[Devin Bowen]] / {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Ashley Fisher]] 6&ndash;3, 7&ndash;5
* It was <U+010C>erm<U+00E1>k's only title of the year and the 3rd of his career. It was Friedl's only title of the year and the 3rd of his career.

